# Experiment Tracking

## Log Entry (YAML)
id, date, status, hypothesis, method, config, results, baseline_comparison, observations, next_step

## Results Table
| Method | Accuracy | Comm Rounds | Cost | Time |
Bold = best. Mean ± std over ≥5 seeds.

## Debug Sequence
1. Sanity check (tiny dataset)
2. Overfit check (train vs val loss)
3. Reproduce published baseline
4. Sweep hyperparameters
5. Check convergence plot

## Fair Comparison Rules
Same compute budget + same data split + same tuning budget + statistical test (p<0.05)

## Experiment Index
experiments/README.md: ID | Date | Method | Key Result | Status
